g3dge7','MG','','5500','4 - 40 SPI ','5/32" Standard','','','','3','1','2','0','','','','','The Merrow MG-3DGE-7 sews a 5/32" stitch at high speed (5500 RPM).  It is a single needle, three-thread machine built on Merrow''s proprietary cam driven architecture, which makes the machine as durable as its stitch is resilient.','The MG-3DGE-7 sews a tight needle stitch using three threads and a unique presser wheel as part of the feed system.  The presser wheel eliminates the hazard of catching in the spaces between the webbing, making the MG-3DGE-7 ideal for nets with loose spacing.  The MG-3DGE-7 also provideds extra looper and needle throw which is essential when sewing heavier material.','The MG-3DGE-7 sews a strong and secure overlock seam on netting at a rate of 4-40 stitches per inch (stand is 8 SPI).  The standard width is 5/32", but this can be increased to 1/4". The stitch wraps the web completely and will not release under impact or when pulled and is wide enough for heavier nets like those used in athletic applications. ','The MG-3DGE-7 shines when seaming loosely spaced mesh and netting, such as lacrosse and hockey nets.  The presser wheel will not catch between the webbing like a standard presser foot. ','','','','72157607123353524','','MERROW 5SDT','MERROW 1SDT-8SDT','A-70-81','6-82-10','97','102','504','','','','','','','','','Merrow M12, 1/2HP, 3450 RPM','','','','Merrow MG-3DGE-7 Sewing Machine for Loosely Space Netting and Mesh','mesh sewing, net sewing, netting sewing, netting seam, netting stitch, netting seaming, mesh seaming, open mesh sewing, loose web sewing, loosely space mesh, large hex mesh sewing, lacrosse net sewing, hockey net sewing, athletic net sewing, sports net sewing','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',4350),(44,0,'6612','','1','','',76797633,'yes','MG-2U','FLAT EDGE EMBLEM MACHINE','The Merrow MG-2U sews a flat finished edge on the edges of emblems.  It is a faster, more refined replacement for embroidery machines that are typically used to sew flat edges on patches and emblems.  ','mg2u','MG','','5500','20 - 40 SPI ','3/32"','','','','2','1','2','0','','','','','The Merrow MG-2U is a 2-thread industrial sewing machine that is ideal for putting edges on emblems and patches. It makes a 5/32" stitch at a standard rate of 28 SPI (though this can be decreased or increased to 20 or 40 SPI respectively), yet even while running at 5500 RPM still operates under 90 dbA. The MG-2U carries a 10 year warranty and is expected to run for years after that with routine care.','The MG-2U uses lightweight moving parts and needle bearings that are manufactured to extremely high tolerances, permitting the fast and smooth starts and stops inherent in intermittent operations like emblem edging. As a result, sewing edges on an MG-3U assures a uniformly finished, unmatched stitch.','The Merrow Edge is the standard bearer for emblem edging. Noticeable for its finish and regularity, the Merrow Emblem Edge is a distinctive mark of quality that can only be made by the Merrow MG Class embleming machine.','The MG-2U is a versatile industrial machine that will satisfy the needs of the local emblem shop to the factory producing thousands of patches per day.\r\n','','','','72157625654494836','500165','MERROW 4SDT','MERROW 3SDT-5SDT','A-70-81','6-82-10','77','100','505','','','','','','','','','Merrow M12, 1/2HP, 3450 RPM','','','','Merrow MG-2U Flat Stitch Industrial Sewing Machine for Edging of Emblems and Patches ','MG-2U, MG2U, flat emblem edge, flat emblem stitch, embroidered edge, flat embroidered edge','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',3160),(39,0,'6612','9','','','',76797649,'no','MG-4D-45','SEWING MACHINE FOR HOSIERY AND LINGERIE','The MG-4D-45 is designed to sew a narrow seam on Athletic Socks or to add a panel seam on lingerie and pantyhose','mg4d45','MG','','5500','20 - 40 SPI ','1/8" - 3/16"','','','','3-6','2','3','0','','','','','The MG-4D-45 is a two-needle, three-thread, serger. Among the best selling hosiery machines in the past 25 years the MG-4D-45 is a versatile machine that sews well on delicate fabrics as well as mid-weight cotton. ','As with all Merrow Machines, the accuracy of the stitch is a critical advantage when sewing high stitch count seams on delicate goods. The MG-4D-45 sews a mock-safety stitch at 5500 RPM with two needles. The wide array of needle plates and presser feet allow customers a great degree of flexibility adjusting the machine to their materials.','The stitch itself is a high count dense stitch that can hold up to wear. Because of the superior engineering the stitch is consistent and will not pucker or lift. As a panel seam for lingerie or for toe closing, it is a very low profile stitch. This makes it suitable for very delicate applications. ',' The applications for this machine generally involve seams that come into contact with the body. Used in factories around the wold for decades, the MG-4D-45 is often found in hosiery production facilities as well as small cottage manufactures around the world','Men''s Hosiery','','','72157606893059633 ','','MERROW B1SDT','MERROW B1SDT-B2SDT','A-70-81','6-82-10','77','100','514','','','','','','','','','Merrow M12, 1/2HP, 3450 RPM','','','','Merrow MG-4D-45 Hosiery Sewing Machine from Merrow','lingerie sewing, toe closing, serger, two needle, merrow, sewing machine','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',3285),(40,0,'6612','2','','','',76797494,'yes','MG-2DNR-1','INDUSTRIAL PURL EDGE SEWING MACHINE','The Merrow Purl Stitching Machine (or merrowing machine) sews a narrow rolled hem on light to mid-weight fabrics. It can be ruffled to create a ''lettuce edge'' look as well. Famous for it''s accuracy, the Merrow Purl edge is unparalleled in the business. ','mg2dnr1','MG','','5500','14 - 40 SPI (22 SPI Standard)','1/16" - 3/16"','','','','2-6','1','2','0','','','','','Merrow has refined the design of it''s signature decorative edging machine over the past 70 years. Designers around the world use the Merrow Purl Machine to sew delicate rolled hems on wedding dresses, lingerie, evening wear and home decor. Built to run at 5500RPM the MG-2DNR-1 will add an unmatched edge at high speed to lightweight and medium weight fabrics. ','The precision of the MG-2DNR-1 is literally unmatched in the sewing machine world. Because of the unique cam drive and the hand crafted looper carrier and needle plate, this Merrow Machine sews a more delicate edge than any other sewing machine manufactured today. At high speed the machine maintains the critical tolerances between needle, needle plate and looper, allowing the product to look beautiful every time. ','The stitch itself is noticably better than imitation purl stitches. A Merrow purl stitch is tighter, it hangs straight on delicates, it appears almost as an extension of the material on which it''s sewn. A Merrow purl stitch is perhaps the most elegant stitch in the world.','Often used in garment factories, sample rooms and custom tailor shops, this machine is now finding it''s way into high-end cottage industries and low volume, high value production facilities.','Purl Stitching','','','72157606889366838','500131','MERROW 2SDT','MERROW 0SDT-4SDT','A-70-81','6-82-10','77','100','502','','','','','','','','','Merrow M12, 1/2HP, 3450 RPM','','','','Merrow MG-2DNR-1 PURL STITCH SEWING MACHINE','MG-2DNR-1, MG2DNR1, MG2DNR-1, 2DNR-1, 2DNR1, Merrow, Purl Stitching, Lettuce Edge, Wedding Sewing ','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',2899),(42,0,'6612','5','4','','',76797564,'yes','MG-3DW-2','INDUSTRIAL SEWING MACHINE FOR SEAMING LIGHT FABRICS','The Merrow MG-3DW-2 is Merrow''s general overseaming machine for lightweight fabrics. Known for its versatility, the MG-3DW-2 has been in daily operation throughout the textile and knitting industries for decades.','mg3dw2','MG','','5500','20 - 40 SPI ','1/8"-1/4" Standard','','','','3-6','1','2','0','','','','','The Merrow MG-3DW-2 is a versatile overlocking machine that sews light to medium weight material.  It is designed to handle everything from "shirt-weight" fabrics to cotton duck and knits, and sews a tight needle stitch on sweaters, dresses, girdles, jackets, bedding, and neckwear.  ','The MG-3DW-2 has wide opening cutters to accommodate multiple types of inserts including crossing elastic sections.  For sewing knit fabric, it can be fitted with coarse feeds and a small needle plate for excellent fabric handling.  ','The MG-3DW-2 is an adaptable machine for general overseaming and sews a tight needle stitch that will accommodate all types of inserts. The standard seam width is 3/16" and it is used for everything from sportwear to canvas bags.  ','The MG-3DW-2 should be used anywhere that quality seaming is required - lightweight sweaters, blankets, sportswear, or outerwear are common applications.','','','','72157607122912878','','MERROW 5SDT','MERROW 1SDT-8SDT','A-70-81','6-82-10','97','102','504','','','','','','','','','Merrow M12, 1/2HP, 3450 RPM','','','','MERROW MG-3DW-2 OVERLOCK SEWING MACHINE','overlock sewing machine, merrow machine, serger, merrowing ','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',3199),(30,0,'70','','','','',0,'no','70-D3B-2 LS-2','TWO THREAD, LOCKED STITCH BUTT SEAMING MACHINE','The Merrow 70-D3B-2 LS is a the worlds best <b>two thread </b>butt seaming machine for light to mid-weight material. Designed to create a locked 16MM (5/8") Stitch the 70-D3B-2 LS is the most reliable way to secure two butt-ends of material','70d3b2ls2','70','','2250','101MM - 305MM (4-12 SPI)','','butt-seam','','','TWO THREAD','1','2','1','','','','','The Merrow 70-D3B-2 LS industrial sewing machine creates a two-thread butted seam on woven and non-woven goods.  The second thread acts as a ''locked-stitch'' and is designed to lock the joining stitches in place. </p><p> The  LS model creates an effective end-end seam for operations that require added security or for fabrics that will undergo a napping process. </p><p> The <? echo $machine; ?> can be configured to produce a butted, gap, or overlap seam to achieve optimum results, according to the fabrics and manufacturing processes used.','The 70-D3B-2 LS uses two threads and a new threading system to create the 16MM (5/8") Locked Stitch. The second thread tension and thread tube are accessible and allow the sewing head to deliver the same reliable performance at 2250RPM. We have modified the base model 70-D3B-2, reducing cost and creating efficiencies for companies that own other versions of the 70-D3B-2','The traditional 16MM (5/8") Butt Seam stitch is ideal for joining fabrics, however in the case the stitch should not be removed (or cannot be compromised) the 70-D3B-2 LS should be used to Lock the Stitch (using two threads). The 70-D3B-2 LS was designed for processes that create significant and unpredictable tension on the seam. \r\n','The 70-D3B-2 LS has been designed for Napping and Shearing processes. It is also used in Billboard construction and hook and look manufacturing. The effectiveness of the locked stitch allows this 70 Class Machine to have <strong> broad appeal to markets outside of textile finishing </strong> (where the stitch is often removed) where joining materials with a PERMANENT FLAT SEAM is desirable.','','','','72157624929046399','500026','MERROW 8SDT','MERROW 3SDT - 8SDT ','','6-82-6','105','72','501','','','','','','','','','','','','','Merrow 70-D3B-2 LS Two Thread Industrial Sewing Machine for Sewing a Locked Stitch on Joined Fabric','merrow, 70-D3B-2 LS, 70d3b2 lock stitch, 70d3b2 ls, 70d3b2ls, 70 Class, 70-D3B-2 Two Thread, merrow machine, industrial sewing machines, sewing machine, industrial sewing machine, end-to-end seaming, fabric joining, textile finishing, seamer, serger, seam welder, welder, seam sealer, sewing seams,end-to-end sewing, merrowing, woven sewing, knitted sewing, non-woven sewing, butted seam, endwise seaming, overlock