d garments','Decorative Shell Edging and Sewing for Baby Garments with Merrow Stitching'),(6,5517,'Military Seaming ','military','Military','Merrow Sewing Machines for Military Garment Sewing Applications','Merrow Sewing Machines sew, edge, and seam a variety of Military Garments, including, badges, patches, uniforms, nomex flight suits, blankets, and gloves','military stitching, military sewing, flightsuit'),(7,5518,'Women''s Garments','womans','womans','Merrow Sewing Machines for Womenâs Garment Sewing Applications','Merrow Industrial Sewing Machines sew distinct stitches on womenâs clothing and garments','purl tank, shell stitch for top of sock, hosiery'),(8,5519,'Home DÃ©cor','home decor','Home Decor','Merrow Sewing Machines for Home Decor Sewing Applications','Merrow Industrial Sewing Machines sew structural and decorative stitches for home dÃ©cor applications ranging from slip cover seams to decorative curtain hems','Sewing Home Decor'),(9,5520,'Netting and Mesh','Netting and Mesh','Netting and Mesh','Merrow Sewing Machines for Netting and Mesh Sewing Applications','Merrow Industrial Sewing Machines sew durable structural seams on mesh nets and laundry bags','Netting and Mesh'),(10,5522,'Athletic Apparel','Athletic Apparel','Athletic Apparel','Merrow Machines for Technical Athletic Apparel Seaming Applications','Merrow sewing machines for athletic apparel applications sew the most technical, durable, and attractive stitches on technical base layers, wool underwear, and fleece garments','technical sewing, athletic apparel sewing, athletic apparel stitch, technical base layer seaming, flatlock stitch, cover stitch, flat stitch, sewing anti-microbial fabric, breathable fabric stitching, '),(11,0,'','','','','',''),(12,5523,'Joining Knit Material','Joining Knit Material','Joining Knit Material','Merrow Butted-Seam Sewing Machines for Joining Knit Fabric End-to-End','Merrow Butted-Seam Sewing Machines sew a wide, flat butted-seam on knits.  They are designed to handle knit fabric, and will sew tubular, jersey, stretch, fleece, and tricot',''),(13,5524,'Joining Non-Wovens','Joining Non-Wovens','Joining Non-Wovens','Merrow Butted-Seam Sewing Machines for Joining Non-Wovens End-to-End','Merrow Butted-Seam Sewing Machines sew a wide, flat butted-seam on non-woven materials such as fiberglass, filter material, automotive foam, rubber, and vinyl leather',''),(14,0,'','','','','',''),(15,6621,'ActiveSeam&#153; Flat Overlock','ActiveSeam&#153;','ActiveSeam&#153; Flat Overlock','Merrow Industrial Sewing Machines for Athletic Apparel and Active Wear','The Merrow MB-4DFO sews three versions of ActiveSeam&#153; Flat Overlock on base and mid layer athletic garments','activeseam, active seam, baselayer, midlayer, base layer, flat overlock, merino wool, replaces flatlock, flatlock replacement, flat lock, flat lock stitch, flat lock replcacement, flat lock alternative, flatlock alternative, merrow flat seam, flat seam, athletic apparel seam, athletic overlock seam,');

